				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Th%E1%BB%B1c/%C3%82n-tri%E1%BB%81u-l%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BA%A5t-th%C3%A1nh-hi%E1%BB%81n-qu%C3%A2n-c%E1%BB%91-%C4%91%C3%B4/poem-KDxOgKAXpzTyzpi3yLLitw">Ân triều lục thất thánh hiền quân cố đô - 殷朝六七聖賢君故都</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author--2pwC2FLqv5BAX5uZnZLaA">Phan Huy Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Gi%C3%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-lGfAWrBsn-3Zi9mT_1tX7w">Đại Giác tự - 大覺寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/author-0k6qEpgf02Latsw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/%C4%90%C4%83ng-B%C3%A0n-A-s%C6%A1n-c%E1%BA%A3m-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-KJpBX0Rm8Tqc-aYjmkLS1Q">Đăng Bàn A sơn cảm hứng - 登盤阿山感興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-M%C6%B0u/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-L%C3%BD-b%C3%A1t-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-p1zLbrSK4nue6Ox-1dOgjA">Đề Lý bát đế tự - 題李八帝寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-M%C6%B0u/author-3hhBDlSkWeBPfZtXuxM8uQ">Phan Trọng Mưu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Th%E1%BB%B1c/H%C3%A0n-Ngu%E1%BB%B5-c%C3%B4ng-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-djaB9RgWeQEdWbR2QqMWmw">Hàn Nguỵ công từ - 韓魏公祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author--2pwC2FLqv5BAX5uZnZLaA">Phan Huy Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%ADch-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-S%C3%A1n/Nam-H%E1%BA%A3i-t%E1%BB%AB-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-agv91UQ4lF8iHoLrEAlBhw">Nam Hải từ vịnh kỳ 1 - 南海祠詠其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%ADch-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-S%C3%A1n/author-raZnRizzmxsn-rfcNRwVcQ">Thích Đại Sán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.